pageContext.claim: “I saved at least 8 Republican Senators, including Mitch, from losing in the last Rigged (for President) Election. Now they (almost all) sit back and watch me fight against a crooked and vicious foe, the Radical Left Democrats. I will NEVER FORGET!”
pageContext.analysis: Sen. Mitch McConnell (R-Ky.), the Senate Republican leader, won in a landslide and did not need Trump's help. The election was not rigged.
